        {"q": "What is NMM and who is it for?", "a": "Network Marketing Master (NMM) is a digital management tool for multi-level marketing (MLM) distributors. It offers contact tracking, AI-powered messaging, and team management in one platform."},
        {"q": "Is the free plan enough?", "a": "Yes, to get started! You can begin with 50 contacts and basic features. As your team grows, upgrading to Pro or Team is easy."},
        {"q": "Is my data secure?", "a": "Yes. All data is stored encrypted on Supabase (PostgreSQL). With Row Level Security, only you can access your data."},
        {"q": "Which network marketing companies does it work with?", "a": "NMM is company-independent. It can be used with Amway, Herbalife, Oriflame, Avon and all MLM companies."},
        {"q": "Is there a mobile app?", "a": "The web app works optimized on all mobile devices. Native iOS/Android apps are on our roadmap."},
